  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/image-1.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>周末继续Regional Park。这个是倒数第二个了。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/image-3.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>难得的好天气，想找一天完全不下雨，真的很难。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/image-2.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>海水清澈。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/image-4.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>走了一圈森林步道，里面不晒，但是冬天有点冷。夏天来应该是刚好。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/image.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
